Resource Profile: CH Core Patient EPR

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/StructureDefinition/ch-core-patient-epr Version: 5.0.0
Active as of 2024-12-17 Computable Name: CHCorePatientEPR

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Definition of the Patient resource for use in the context of the electronic patient record (EPR). It is used to include the patient in an EPR document (referenced in Composition/DocumentReference).

Core patient demographics which can be shared

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH Core Composition EPR and CH Core DocumentReference EPR
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Patient/MaxMuster
